      "name": "<think>\nThe user wants me to translate \"Amphibious\" from English to Simplified Chinese (zh-CN).\n\n\"Amphibious\" in English means:\n1. Relating to or affecting both land and water\n2. (of a vehicle or person) able to operate on both land and water\n\nIn Chinese, this translates to:\n\"两栖的\" (liǎng qī de)\n\nFor example:\n- Amphibious vehicle = 两栖车辆\n- Amphibious operation = 两栖作战\n\nSince the domain is \"item.name\" (物品名称), the translation should be the standard term for this type of item/category.\n</think>\n\n两栖的",
